OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774361471
OL,3,CSwapping L plates for skates as
OL,4,Cpermission granted for new park
OL,6,FPlanning permission has been granted
OL,7,Fto build a new skate park in the
OL,8,Fcentre of St Helier.
OL,10,FIt will be built on South Hill - over
OL,11,Fa set of reversing bays currently used
OL,12,Fby learner drivers.
OL,14,FIt is hoped the development will
OL,15,Fprovide an accessible skating facility
OL,16,Fin the east of the island for those
OL,17,Fwho cannot easily get to the existing
OL,18,Fpark at Les Quennevais, which opened
OL,19,Fin 2023.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774361471
OL,3,CSwapping L plates for skates as
OL,4,Cpermission granted for new park
OL,6,FThe facility will, however, only be
OL,7,Ftemporary - with the equipment
OL,8,Feventually moving to Fort Regent as
OL,9,Fpart of that area's major
OL,10,Fredevelopment plans.
OL,12,FThe South Hill site will subsequently
OL,13,Fbe converted into a cycle park, which
OL,14,Fthe island's Infrastructure Department
OL,15,Fsays "ensures there is long-term
OL,16,Fcommunity benefit".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774361471
OL,3,CSwapping L plates for skates as
OL,4,Cpermission granted for new park
OL,6,FThe plans have been developed after a
OL,7,Fseries of consultations with the
OL,8,FJersey Skateparks Association, Driver
OL,9,Fand Vehicle Standards, and other
OL,10,Fcommunity groups.
OL,12,FIn a statement, Constable Andy Jehan,
OL,13,Fthe island's Minister for
OL,14,FInfrastructure, explains the site
OL,15,Fallows them "to provide a much-needed
OL,16,Ffacility for young people and families
OL,17,Fin St Helier".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
