FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774361471
OL,3,CSwapping L plates for skates as
OL,4,Cpermission granted for new park
OL,6,FHe adds: "The project team has worked
OL,7,Fcarefully with stakeholders to ensure
OL,8,Fthe design is safe, considerate of
OL,9,Fneighbours, and aligned with our
OL,10,Flonger-term plans for Fort Regent.
OL,12,F"This skate park is an important step
OL,13,Fin meeting community needs and
OL,14,Foffering a positive space for active,
OL,15,Fhealthy recreation."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
